2. The St. Catherine Parish Council shall exercise, in respect of the
Municipality of Portmore, the powers of the Parish Council or Competent
Authority, as the case may require, specified in the following Acts-
      (a) The Burial Within Towns' Limits Act;
      (6) The Keeping of Animals Act;
      (c) The Poor Relief Act;
      (4 The Pound Act; and
      (e) The Public Cemetery Management and Regulation Act.
